Evolution 2.28.0 2009-09-20
----------------------------

Notable changes for 2.28.0 release,
	Google Calendar uses caldav interface.
	Select the local Ical files as calendar source
	Configurable Date formats
	Better system timezone discovery
	Attachment bar rewrite
	Re-add support for volder of vfolders
	GroupWise meeting retract/resend 

Bug Fixes:
Calendar:
	#582780 - Use proxy in Google calendar setup plugin (Alexander Klepikov)
	#581602 - Purge calendar function not working (Milan Crha)
	#594407 - Alarms won't go away (Milan Crha)
Mailer:
	#572960 - Ignore and drop invalid signatures on load (Milan Crha)
	#594609 - Date field in message list shows incorrect "x days ago" (Chenthill Palanisamy)
	#594628 - Switching back from Outgoing filters to Incoming filters does not
		  show existing incoming filters (Chenthill Palanisamy)
Miscellaneous:
	Documentation update for 2.28.0 release (Akhil Laddha)

Translations:
	Žygimantas Beručka (lt)
