	- Exchange Folder size support (Sarfraaz)
	- Exchange Subscribe/Unsubscribe support (Shakti Sen)
	- Exchange Folder Permissions support (Shakti Sen)
	- Exchange Delegation support (Praveen Kumar)	- 
